**Mobile-Specific Styles:**
```css
/* Mobile touch targets */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .doc-tabs button {
    @apply px-4 py-3 min-h-[44px]; /* Touch-friendly */
  }

  .doc-section h2 {
    @apply text-xl; /* Smaller headings on mobile */
  }

  .prose {
    @apply text-base; /* Optimal reading size */
  }

  /* Hide complex tables on mobile, show simplified version */
  .prose table {
    @apply text-sm;
  }
}

