- [ ] Hamburger menu for mobile sidebar navigation
- [ ] Collapsible table of contents on tablet
- [ ] Full-screen modal on mobile devices
- [ ] Swipe gestures for modal dismiss (optional)
- [ ] Responsive typography (text scales appropriately)
- [ ] Horizontal scroll for wide code blocks/tables
- [ ] Mobile-optimized search (full-screen on mobile)
- [ ] Test on iOS Safari and Android Chrome
- [ ] Ensure no horizontal scroll on small screens

